attributes.name: Blueberry Dream 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Blueberry Dream is a hybrid strain that combines the genetics of Blueberryand Haze strains. It typically has a sweet and fruity aroma with hints of blueberry. This strain offers a balanced high, providing both a relaxed body sensation and a euphoric cerebral effect.

attributes.name: Gorilla Glue #4 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Gorilla Glue #4, also known as GG4, is a potent hybrid strain renowned for its strong and long-lasting effects. It often has a pungent, earthy aroma with notes of pine and chocolate. Gorilla Glue #4 induces a heavy-bodied relaxation, accompanied by an uplifting and euphoric mental buzz.

attributes.name: GMO 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: GMO, short for Garlic, Mushroom, and Onion, is an indica-dominant hybrid strain with a distinct and pungent aroma reminiscent of its name. It typically offers a combination of savory and earthy flavors. GMO is known for its potent effects, including deep relaxation, euphoria, and potential appetite stimulation.

attributes.name: Guava 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Guava is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain that typically has a tropical and fruity aroma with notes of guava. It offers a relaxing and calming high, promoting deep physical relaxation, stress relief, and potential pain management. Guava is known for its pleasant flavor and potential mood elevation.

attributes.name: White Fire OG 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: White Fire OG, also known as WiFi OG, is a hybrid strain that combines the genetics of Fire OG and The White. It generally has a pungent, diesel-like aroma with earthy undertones. White Fire OG provides a powerful and uplifting cerebral high along with deep relaxation and potential pain relief.

attributes.name: AiroPod - Durban Poison - Sativa - .5g
attributes.body:
AiroPod Strain Series .5g Cartridge

• Strain Series

• Sativa

• Durban Poison

• Pure Distillate Oil

• Full Terpene Profile

• High Potency

 

The AiroPod cartridge is more than a stylish magnet, it’s the first vessel of its kind. The secured mouthpiece and filling septum minimize the possibility of leakage, something which has been a common issue among older model vaporizers. Considering that risk of accidental exposure, to children or pets for example, the AiroPod cartridge was built for safety as well as durability.

Free from a traditional wick and coil setup, AiroPod cartridges adopted ceramic reactor technology to serve as the heating element. Unmatched thermal precision ensures concentrates are always vaporized at the proper temperature. This preserves the flavor of concentrates and prevents them from burning. The silver-plated magnetic base makes exchanging cartridges a snap, while ensuring a solid connection every time.

attributes.name: KulluKush 1 Gram Tank - Grape Goji OG
attributes.body:
Introducing the Kullukush 1 gram Tank in the Grape Goji OG strain from Multitude Manufacturing. This tank is filled with a premium filtered distillate with over 90 percent THC potency and infused with a custom blend of live and botanical terpenes. This tank is designed to provide you with a convenient and enjoyable cannabis experience. It's the pinnacle of potency and quality with the Kullukush Tank in the high-end I-Krusher ceramic reservoir.

Known for its potent, euphoric, and relaxing effects, this tank offers a delightful combination of sweet grape and rose flavors. With each puff, you'll experience a smooth and flavorful vapor that captures the essence of this popular strain.
